oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Bicentennial Mall State Park Pathway of History
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Color photograph of five monoliths from the Pathway of History located inside Bicentennial Mall State Park in Nashville, Tennessee. The Tennessee State Capitol is visible in the background. Features a divided back, title, and a semi-transparent logo for the state park on reverse. [No. 327610] Note: this is an additional copy of this postcard and is the same as 48775.
